## 🌐 OSI Model

| Layer       | Purpose          |
| ----------- | ---------------- |
| Application | User interaction |
| Transport   | Reliability      |
| Network     | Routing          |
| Data Link   | MAC delivery     |
| Physical    | Signals          |

---

## 🌐 TCP vs UDP

| TCP      | UDP       |
| -------- | --------- |
| Reliable | Fast      |
| ACK used | No ACK    |
| Ordered  | Unordered |

---

## 🌐 DNS

Domain → IP mapping

Example:

```id="zplfdk"
google.com → IP
```

---

## 🌐 NAT

Many private IPs → one public IP

---

## 🌐 HTTP vs HTTPS

HTTP → plain
HTTPS → encrypted

