# 🧠 MCQ PRACTICE (Week 1 Day 1)

---

## MCQ 1

Which layer handles routing?

A) Session
B) Transport
C) Network
D) Physical

✅ Answer: C

---

## MCQ 2

Which protocol is reliable?

A) UDP
B) TCP
C) IP
D) ARP

✅ Answer: B

---

## MCQ 3

DNS converts:

A) IP → MAC
B) Name → IP
C) Port → IP
D) MAC → IP

✅ Answer: B

---

## MCQ 4

Which is connectionless?

A) TCP
B) UDP
C) HTTP
D) HTTPS

✅ Answer: B

---

## MCQ 5

What does HTTPS add?

A) Routing
B) Encryption
C) Switching
D) Fragmentation

✅ Answer: B

